{"slug":"sirkuler-26-0276","reference":"Sirkuler_26_0276","gazette":"06 Mayıs 2026 Tarihli ve 33245 Sayılı Resmî Gazete","title":"Yeni Bitki Karantinası Yönetmeliği Yayımlandı – İthalat, İhracat, Transit ve Serbest Bölge İşlemlerine İlişkin Kapsamlı Düzenlemeler Getirildi","date":"06 Mayıs 2026","bodyHtml":"<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Tarım ve Orman Bakanlığı tarafından\r\nhazırlanan yeni “Bitki Karantinası Yönetmeliği” yayımlanmış olup, bitki,\r\nbitkisel ürün ve diğer maddelerin ithalat, ihracat, transit ve serbest bölge\r\nişlemlerine ilişkin bitki sağlığı uygulamaları yeniden düzenlenmiştir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Yeni Yönetmelik ile özellikle;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Bitki\r\nsağlığı kontrollerinin kapsamı, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Bitki Sağlık\r\nSertifikası uygulamaları, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">BKKTS (Bitki\r\nKarantinası Kayıt ve Takip Sistemi) işlemleri, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Transit ve\r\nserbest bölge uygulamaları, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Zararlı\r\norganizma tespit prosedürleri, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Ahşap\r\nambalaj malzemelerine ilişkin ISPM 15 uygulamaları, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Geri dönen\r\neşya işlemleri, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Yeniden\r\nihracat (Re-Export) süreçleri <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">ayrıntılı şekilde yeniden düzenlenmiştir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Yönetmelikte öne çıkan başlıca düzenlemeler\r\naşağıda yer almaktadır:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Bitki,\r\nbitkisel ürün ve diğer maddelerin giriş, çıkış ve transit işlemlerinin\r\ntamamının BKKTS üzerinden yürütülmesi hüküm altına alınmıştır. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">İthalatta\r\nresmî kontroller; belge kontrolü, beyan kontrolü ve bitki sağlığı kontrolü\r\nolmak üzere üç aşamalı hale getirilmiştir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Bitki\r\nSağlığı Dolaşım Belgesi uygulaması detaylandırılarak, giriş noktasında kontrolü\r\ntamamlanamayan ürünlerin başka yetkili giriş noktalarına veya onaylı kontrol\r\nyerlerine sevki için yeni usuller belirlenmiştir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">ISPM 15\r\nstandartlarına uygun olmayan ahşap ambalaj malzemelerinin ülkeye girişine izin\r\nverilmeyeceği düzenlenmiştir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Elektronik\r\nBitki Sağlık Sertifikalarının kabulüne ilişkin hükümler güncellenmiştir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Zararlı risk\r\nanalizine tabi ürünler için risk değerlendirme ve ithalat izin süreçleri\r\nyeniden tanımlanmıştır. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Karantinaya\r\ntabi zararlı organizma tespiti halinde sevkiyatın engellenmesi, iadesi ve\r\nbildirim süreçleri ayrıntılı şekilde düzenlenmiştir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Yolcu\r\nberaberinde getirilen ürünler, posta/kargo gönderileri ve serbest bölge\r\nişlemlerine ilişkin özel hükümler getirilmiştir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Geri dönen\r\nürünler ile yeniden ihracat (Re-Export) işlemlerinde uygulanacak kontrol ve\r\nsertifikasyon süreçleri yeniden yapılandırılmıştır. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Bitki Sağlık\r\nSertifikalarının düzenlenme, geçerlilik, yenileme ve iptal şartları ayrıntılı\r\nolarak belirlenmiştir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Analiz,\r\nnumune alma ve itiraz süreçlerine ilişkin yeni prosedürler düzenlenmiştir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Ayrıca Yönetmelik ile;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">03.12.2011\r\ntarihli ve 28131 sayılı Resmî Gazete’de yayımlanan eski Bitki Karantinası\r\nYönetmeliği yürürlükten kaldırılmıştır. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Yeni\r\nYönetmelik yayımı tarihinden itibaren 90 gün sonra yürürlüğe girecektir</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">. <o:p></o:p></span>